      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable and stylish ride? This well-maintained vehicle is in great shape and ready for the road! It has been cared for conscientiously, showing only the minor signs of use you'd expect from a car that's been enjoyed. It runs smoothly and looks fantastic, making it a perfect choice for anyone seeking quality and value.",
