    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. It is currently not in reliable running order, as the engine suffers from a severe knock and the transmission fails to engage properly in higher gears. The exterior shows extensive rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This car is being sold strictly as-is and would be best suited as a donor vehicle for parts or for someone looking for a very intensive restoration project.",
