    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for an ambitious restoration project or as a comprehensive donor for parts. The engine currently struggles to maintain a consistent idle and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping, indicating that major mechanical repairs are likely necessary. Visually, the car shows its age with significant rust on the lower panels, several deep dents, and a faded paint job. The interior requires a complete overhaul, as the upholstery is heavily worn and several electronic components are non-functional. While it is not currently road-ready, it remains a complete vehicle for someone with the tools and time to bring it back to life.",
      "price": 5500.0,
